rows.label: qst201403_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, I see you haven't run away yet.
Well done. I'm proud of you.

rows.label: qst201403_msg0002
rows.name:
Au contraire, my little croissant. It is I
who am proud of you.

rows.label: qst201403_msg0003
rows.name:
I thought you'd be turning tail at the
threat of taking on my relentless
Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201403_msg0004
rows.name:
You'd better not underestimate me,
Zakuro!

rows.label: qst201403_msg0005
rows.name:
You're the one that's going to be
routed by my awesome Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201403_msg0008
rows.name:
Well, since we've agreed that we're
going to put our Girl Power to the test,
we need to decide how.

rows.label: qst201403_msg0010
rows.name:
Indeed we must.
Actually, I haven't given
it much thought...

rows.label: qst201403_msg0012
rows.name:
We'll get a few people to act as judges.
It'll be their job to decide who's got
the most Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201403_msg0013
rows.name:
And it'll be our job to each persuade
them we have more of it than the other
one does!

rows.label: qst201403_msg0018
rows.name: Does that sound fair to you?

rows.label: qst201403_msg0014
rows.name:
Oh, absolutely. I love girl talk. I'm
very confident about this.

rows.label: qst201403_msg0015
rows.name:
Okay! Let's grab someone walking by.
Then the real battle can begin!

rows.label: qst201403_msg0017
rows.name: What? This is a piece of cake!
